      "text": "Un uhs to Rekabiteru Nammu fazzija Jeremijus: Ta fakka tas KUNGS Zebaoṭ/ tas Israëka Deews: Tadeht ka juhs effat klaustijschi to Baufli Jona- daba juhta Tehva/ un targaj- tehi wiſſas winna Pawehlefcha- nas/ un darrijschi wiſſu/ ko wiſſch jums bij pawehlejis."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tadeht ta fakka tas KUNGS Zebaoṭ/ tas Israëka Deews: Jonadabam Rekaba Dehlan ne truhks weens Wihrs/ kas manna Preefschâ stahw wiſ- fá Laika."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XXXVI. Nodalla.\nJeremijus leek us Deewa Pawehlefchanu wiſ- fus sawus Wahrdus weenâ Grahmata ee rakstiht : 1/ 2. Bahruks laffa to preefsch teem Laudim/ un preefsch ta Rehnina Jojaki ma : 5/ 24. Kas to Grahmatn fagreesch un fadesina : 20. Bet Deews paweht tam Praweetam zittu Grahmatu rakstiht : 27. Un tam Jojakimam weenu breefnigu Nah wi fluddinaht : 29."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "N zettorta Gaddâ Jo- jakima/ ta Dehta Josi- jus/ ta Rehnina no Ju- da/ notikke fchis Wahrdus us Je- remiju no ta KUNGA/ kas fazztija:"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jeminees fewtim weenu Grahmatu / un raksti us to wiſſus Wahrdus/ ko es us tewi efmu runnajs pahr Israëtu / un pahr Juhda/ un pahr wiſſahm tahmZautahn/no tahs Deenas/ ka es us tewi efmu runnajs/ no tahm Deenahm Josijus lihds chodeen."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jaschu tee no ta Nanuna Juhda klaufs wiſſu to Launu-"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "nu / ko es teem dohmaju richt/ ka tee atgreeschahs, itw no fawa nifna Zetta/ un es no Noseegumu/ un winnu E kuß peedohmu."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad aizinaja Jerem Bahruku Nerijus Dehlu/ Bahruks rakstija no Jerem Muttes wiſſus Wahrdus KUNGA/ ko wiſſch us to runnajs/ weenâ Grahmata."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jeremijus paweh Bahrukam/ un fazztija : Es pu apturrehts/ ka es ne wa eeksch ta KUNGA Namma"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu tad eij/ un lahti tahs Grahmatas/ ko tu efti mannas Muttes rakstijs KUNGA Wahrdus/ preefsch Jaschu Autim ta KUN Namma/ tai Gawefchanas D nâ/ ir preefsch wiſſa Juhda fim/ kas no faweem Pills teem nahk/ buhs tew tohs laffi"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jaschu tee Seimne met fees/ un peeluhgs ta KUNG Breefscha/ un atgreesifees katrs no fawa nifna Zetta/ jo Dufiniba un ta Bahrsiba leela/ ko tas KUNGS pre"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Bahruks Neriju Dehts darrija pehz wiſſu/ ko ta Praweets Jeremijus winna bij pawehlejs/ un laffija no tah Grahmatas ta KUNGA Wah dus eeksch ta KUNGA Nain"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tas notikke peckta Gad da Jojakima ta Dehta Josijus ta Rehnina no Juhda/ dewit Met"
    }
  ],
